* Bootstrap Switch — DUT subcircuit
* 180nm PTM, parameterised W/L/CB
*
* Ports: VIN CLKS VDD VOUT
*   VIN  — analog input
*   CLKS — sampling clock (HIGH = sample, LOW = reset)
*   VDD  — supply
*   VOUT — sampled output (connect to sampling capacitor)

.subckt bootstrap_switch VIN CLKS VDD VOUT

* ── Inverter (CLKS → CLKSB) ────────────────────────────────────────────────
MP_INV CLKSB CLKS VDD  VDD  pmos W={W_inv_p}u L={L}
MN_INV CLKSB CLKS 0    0    nmos W={W_inv_n}u L={L}

* ── Sampling switch ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
MS     VOUT  VGATE VIN  0    nmos W={W_sw}u L={L}

* ── Bootstrap capacitor ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
CB     CB_TOP CB_BOT {CB}

* ── Reset switches ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
* M1: PMOS, charges CB top plate to VDD during reset (VGATE=0 → M1 ON)
M1     CB_TOP VGATE VDD  CB_TOP pmos W={W_m1}u L={L}

* M2: NMOS, discharges CB bottom plate to GND during reset
M2     CB_BOT CLKSB 0    0    nmos W={W_m2}u L={L}

* ── VGATE pull-down (reset) ────────────────────────────────────────────────
* M5A+M5 cascode: pulls VGATE to ~VDD-Vth during reset, protects M5 from Vds>VDD
M5A    VGATE  VDD   NET_5A  0    nmos W={W_m5a}u L={L}
M5     NET_5A CLKSB  0      0    nmos W={W_m5}u  L={L}

* ── Top-plate conduction (sampling) ────────────────────────────────────────
* M4: PMOS, connects CB top plate to VGATE during sampling
M4     VGATE  NET_G4 CB_TOP CB_TOP pmos W={W_m4}u L={L}

* M4A: NMOS, connects VIN to M4 gate during sampling (via VGATE)
M4A    NET_G4 VGATE  VIN    0    nmos W={W_m4a}u L={L}

* M4B: PMOS, pre-charges M4 gate to VDD during reset
M4B    NET_G4 CLKS   VDD    VDD  pmos W={W_m4b}u L={L}

* M4C: NMOS, startup — pulls M4 gate low when CLKS rises
M4C    NET_G4 CLKS   CB_BOT 0    nmos W={W_m4c}u L={L}

* ── VIN-to-CB bottom (sampling) ────────────────────────────────────────────
* M3: NMOS, connects VIN to CB bottom during sampling (gate=VGATE=VIN+VDD)
M3     CB_BOT VGATE  VIN    0    nmos W={W_m3}u L={L}

.ends bootstrap_switch
